      "title": "Establishment of an entangled atom-field state in the Jaynes-Cummings model",
      "abstract": "We use the eigenstates of the reduced density operators to give an explicit form of the entangled atom-field state in the Jaynes-Cummings model. We relate the expansion coefficients to physical quantities and discuss the effect of atomic coherence on this entangled state."
